education program for gifted youth overview courses ohs summer schools apply and register home software research news contact epgy login course catalog english secondary level eg20 grammar of the sentence eg21 grammar of the sentence ii course contents lectures exercises virtual classroom eg21 grammar and style of the sentence ii eg21 is a self paced web based course designed to further the principles of grammar and style learned in eg20 the course consists of a series of lessons followed by interactive exercises students watch lectures on subject verb agreement prepositions pronouns modifiers and punctuation and complete the accompanying exercises which will be either instantly evaluated by the program or automatically submitted to the instructor who reviews work and returns feedback as needed
